a:r.a:t: Large, flexibles pet care division serving bird food, cat food, dog food and treats
Current focus on lids / peelable membranes
Dry pet care offering including flexible materials such as substrates of PET, die-cut capsules, various foils and retort lids
Seeking additional flexible packaging targets after recent divestiture
Product offering includes multiwall paper packaging, flexible plastic packaging, woven polypropylene bags and specialty coated materials
Primary component of business focus on pet care end-market
Offering ranges from plastic and paper-based bags, stand-up pouches, shelf-ready packaging and corrugated cases
Pet care packaging prominently noted as area of focus
Offers stand up pouches, shaped pouches, retort pouches, surface printed films and laminated films for the pet care industry
Recently rolled out two new pet care packaging applications
Manufactures and sells industrial and consumer packaging products
Strong focus on pet care end-market, offering flexible solutions for treats and dry food including easy-open /re-closeable bags and pouches
Provides pouches, stand-up pouches, overwrap bags, lidding and rollstock for pet care, food & beverage and personal care markets
Actively seeking flexible packaging acquisition targets
Pouches, bags and rollstock for grooming products, toys, vitamins and supplements made of flexible materials to replace glass alternatives
Recently noted flexible pouches as “major win” for the company
The company’s Lifestyle and Industrial Supplies segment provides packaging products, including pet care
Has made U.S. acquisitions in the past to expand footprint
Leading provider of flexible packaging solutions such as pouches, bulk bags and rollstock for customers to improve brand recognition
Continue to make significant investments to grow inorganically
Manufactures plastic and paper packaging products including retail bags, multi-layer packaging solutions and stand up pouches
Recent acquisition increased sheet and film product offering
Offers flexible packaging products such as roll
stocks, premade bags, pouches, lidding solutions and labels
Extensive pet care offerings and strong financial wherewithal
Leading provider of flexible and paper based-packaging solutions for the food safety, facility hygiene and product protection industries
